main.name: Somelina Obiechina
main.bio: Software Developer with a proven track record in full-stack software development and systems support. Brings over three years of experience optimizing technology processes in healthcare, legal, and academic settings—including managing web platforms, building responsive applications, troubleshooting system workflows, and supporting diverse teams. Skilled in React, JavaScript, Python, and WordPress, with hands-on expertise in user experience, data security, and digital accessibility. Adept at translating complex requirements into effective, user-friendly solutions that improve efficiency and service delivery. Currently pursuing a master’s in computer and information technology from the University of Pennsylvania.
